author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: HUF Reveals New Pink Panther Collection Releasing This Week
text:
Visit the original post to see all 11 images from this gallery. 
Brand: HUF
Season: SS17
Key Pieces: White coaches jacket, pink socks, baby blue hoodie, tie-dye T-shirt.
Editor’s Notes: HUF is celebrating the spirit of the sly cat, the Pink Panther, with a collaborative capsule collection consisting of apparel and accessories. The character can here be seen on everything from T-shirts and hoodies, to jackets, hats, socks and stickers.
With pieces ranging from $10 USD to $300 USD, you can look forward to HUF’s Pink Panther assortment arriving on March 30 at HUF retailers and online .
For more must-see fashion, take a look at every piece from Kanye’s new adidas “Calabasas” collection.
